</style><h3 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading">对二十二集、ANYCOLOR的批判态度及部分汇总网站散播不实谣言</h3><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="ArN6hWvCe2"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/some-video-contributor-and-roundup-blogs-criticized-the-design-of-nijisanji-merch-as-being-very-similar-to-other-works/">有视频投稿人/总结网站VTuber批评二三吉的商品设计与其他作品非常相似</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“一些视频贡献者/摘要网站 VTuber 批评 Nijisanji 商品的设计与其他作品非常相似” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/some-video-contributor-and-roundup-blogs-criticized-the-design-of-nijisanji-merch-as-being-very-similar-to-other-works/embed/#?secret=CWieZ4LQtW#?secret=ArN6hWvCe2" data-secret="ArN6hWvCe2" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="FmYE89EkHF"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/some-roundup-blogs-unilaterally-criticize-the-group-over-treatment-of-indonesian-and-korean-vtuber-affiliating-to-nijisanji/">部分摘要网站Nijisanji单方面批评该组织对印尼和韩国VTubers的待遇</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“同组对属于 Nijisanji 的印度尼西亚和韩国 VTuber 的待遇进行了片面批评​​” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/some-roundup-blogs-unilaterally-criticize-the-group-over-treatment-of-indonesian-and-korean-vtuber-affiliating-to-nijisanji/embed/#?secret=tdk4K6k1li#?secret=FmYE89EkHF" data-secret="FmYE89EkHF" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-conten